{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Render Item Columns\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This package provides a gui interface to render columns of selected items. Has optional tail length, rename capabilities, and its also possible to add regions based on item columns. GUI created using Lokasenna's GUI 2.0. https://forum.cockos.com/showthread.php?t=177772\par}
