{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Opens the folder containing Reaper's executable file.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Opens the folder containing Reaper's resources (effects, scripts, etc)\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Provides a circular "quick menu" for commonly-used actions, similar to how weapons are selected in many FPS games.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Use the accompanying script "Lokasenna_Radial Menu Setup.lua" to configure the menu and additional settings.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 See the forum thread for further documentation/bug reports/help.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Allows action IDs to repeated at a specified interval\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab This script won't do anything by itself; use the included script 'Lokasenna_Repeat Action - Add new action.lua' to generate a script for each action you want to repeat.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab In Reaper's action list, use the 'Load' button and browse to: 'Reaper/Scripts/ReaTeam Scripts/Various/Lokasenna_Repeat Action/"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Select the scripts you generated.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Each script will be individually accessible in the action list for you to bind to a shortcut key.\sa180\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Scrolls the mixer so that the first selected track is at the left-hand side, if possible.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Tool that shows cursor position in relation to the item take's Source time\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab remembers last position and window size\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab resizeable via mouse-wheel\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab edit cursor can be moved to any user-defined source time position\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab directory where source file resides can be opened in explorer/finder\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab tooltips\sa180\par}
}

